    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my reliable ride. It\u2019s been such a great car for me, always getting me where I need to go without a hitch! It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super clean inside and it still drives like a dream. It's the perfect fit for someone who wants a dependable vehicle that still looks and feels great on the open road. I've taken really good care of it, and I'd love to see it go to a good home. Come take it for a spin, I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This unit delivers exceptional throttle response via its factory individual throttle bodies and is paired with a desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis has been proactively maintained, featuring rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to ensure precise variable valve timing. The suspension maintains its factory composure with refreshed bushings and a limited-slip variable M differential that provides excellent lateral grip. While the finish shows minor evidence of its 8,000 RPM heritage, the rod bearings have been serviced, and the cooling system is fully pressurized and leak-free. This is a driver\u2019s specimen optimized for peak longitudinal and lateral acceleration.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Runs well. Inspections welcome.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
